<h3>Require Vehicle Entry</h3>

<p>You have the ability to <i>force</i> the customer to <b>select their vehicle before they can proceed with checkout</b>. If enabled, it will automatically do it for products that have vehicles mapped to them. Upon selecting add to cart, if they do not already have a vehicle selected in their session, but there are vehicles <b>available for the selected product</b>, they will be redirected to the intermediate page.</p>

