<p>On the intermediate page the customer is presented with a chained select-box interface exactly like the main vehicle search, but <b>only populated with the vehicles for the selected product</b>. The customer must enter in the vehicle before proceeding with checkout. This ensures the customer has a chance to verify compatability. This feature is completely optional and if enabled will only appear where it makes sense.</p>